title: ARIZONA CARDINALS - WHEEL OF TEAMS
itunes:title: ARIZONA CARDINALS - WHEEL OF TEAMS
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including the latest update with the Rooney Rule, Taysom Hills role with the Saints, and Fitzmagic helping Tua learn the ropes. As chosen by the wheel, the hereos deep dive into the Arizona Cardinals and chat with Darren Urban from azcardinals.com to talk about the Hopkins trade and what Vance Joseph has in mind with his new acquisitions.
